      <span>зі»з»ҹиҝҗиЎҢдёӯ</span>
      <span style="margin-left:auto;white-space:nowrap"><span class="sd-wc-badge">2026 дё–з•ҢжқҜзүҲ</span></span>
    </div>
  </div><div class="sd-body">
        <div class="sd-nav-item" onclick="switchNav('home')" data-nav="home">
