              <span class="bt-stat amber">е‘ҪдёӯзҺҮ <span class="bt-num">67.2%</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bt-stat-item">
            <div class="bt-month">рҹ“Ҡ 2026е№ҙ4жңҲ</div>
            <div class="bt-row">
              <span class="bt-stat blue">еңәж¬Ў <span class="bt-num">62</span></span>
              <span class="bt-stat green">е‘Ҫдёӯ <span class="bt-num">41</span></span>
              <span class="bt-stat amber">е‘ҪдёӯзҺҮ <span class="bt-num">66.1%</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bt-stat-item">
            <div class="bt-month">рҹ“Ҡ 2026е№ҙ3жңҲ</div>
            <div class="bt-row">
              <span class="bt-stat blue">еңәж¬Ў <span class="bt-num">55</span></span>
              <span class="bt-stat green">е‘Ҫдёӯ <span class="bt-num">36</span></span>
              <span class="bt-stat amber">е‘ҪдёӯзҺҮ <span class="bt-num">65.5%</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bt-stat-item">
            <div class="bt-month">рҹ“Ҡ 2026е№ҙ2жңҲ</div>
            <div class="bt-row">
              <span class="bt-stat blue">еңәж¬Ў <span class="bt-num">48</span></span>
              <span class="bt-stat green">е‘Ҫдёӯ <span class="bt-num">31</span></span>
              <span class="bt-stat amber">е‘ҪдёӯзҺҮ <span class="bt-num">64.6%</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bt-stat-item">
            <div class="bt-month">рҹ“Ҡ 2026е№ҙ1жңҲ</div>
            <div class="bt-row">
              <span class="bt-stat blue">еңәж¬Ў <span class="bt-num">51</span></span>
              <span class="bt-stat green">е‘Ҫдёӯ <span class="bt-num">33</span></span>
              <span class="bt-stat amber">е‘ҪдёӯзҺҮ <span class="bt-num">64.7%</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top:5px;padding:6px 10px;font-size:10px;color:var(--t3);text-align:center;border-top:1px solid rgba(66,165,245,.06)">
            рҹ“Ҳ иҝ‘5дёӘжңҲз»јеҗҲе‘ҪдёӯзҺҮ <span style="color:var(--green);font-weight:600">65.7%</span>
            <span style="color:var(--t3);font-size:9px">пјҲ274еңә / е‘Ҫдёӯ180еңәпјү</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><div class="acc" id="accDoc">
      <div class="acc-head" onclick="toggleAccordion('accDoc')">
        <span class="acc-arrow">в–¶</span>
        <span class="acc-icon">рҹ“ҳ</span>
        <span class="acc-label">зі»з»ҹиҜҙжҳҺд№Ұ</span>
