<h2 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--cyan);margin:20px 0 10px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,.12)">дёғгҖҒиҙҙеҗҲеәҰиҜ„еҲҶеҸӮж•°</h2>
